Prerequisite: Asio Library
    apt-get install libasio-dev #(on Ubuntu)

Here are the different command lines to build the examples

    make tcp_server
    make tcp_client

    make udp_server
    make udp_client

You can build all of tcp or udp using these

    make tcp
    make udp

You also have the possibility to build all, clean and show help

    make all
    make clean
    make help

